# Booking — Schedule Closure endpoints
# UC-010a (create), UC-010b (remove), list
# TenantContext populated from X-Tenant-ID / X-Actor-ID headers (set by BFF).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl   = {{backendUrl}}
@closureId = {{createClosure.response.body.id}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — list closures
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List closures in December 2026
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures?from=2026-12-01&to=2026-12-31
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — create full-day closure (UC-010a)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Create a full-day holiday closure
# @name createClosure
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "date": "2026-12-25",
  "reason": "HOLIDAY",
  "notes": "Natal"
}

###

### Create a partial closure (maintenance 10:00–12:00)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "date": "2026-12-26",
  "reason": "MAINTENANCE",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "12:00",
  "notes": "Manutenção preventiva"
}

###

### Create a staff day off (full day)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: STAFF

{
  "date": "2026-12-27",
  "reason": "STAFF_DAY_OFF"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — remove closure (UC-010b)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Remove a closure
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures/{{closureId}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### 403 — CUSTOMER role not allowed
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: CUSTOMER
X-Actor-Role: CUSTOMER

{
  "date": "2026-12-28",
  "reason": "HOLIDAY"
}

###

### 422 — Past date
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "date": "2020-01-01",
  "reason": "HOLIDAY"
}

###

### 409 — Date already closed (duplicate)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "date": "2026-12-25",
  "reason": "MAINTENANCE"
}

###

### 404 — Closure not found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000099
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 400 — Invalid date format
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule/closures
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "date": "25-12-2026",
  "reason": "HOLIDAY"
}
